Would I like to know something? (Dilatory sip and lip lick.) Well, atall my five public readings since the first on September 3, 1928, in theSalle Planiol, she had been present, she had applauded till her palms(showing palms) ached, and had made up her mind that next time she'd besmart and plucky enough to push her way through the crowd (yes, crowd--noneed to smile ironically) with the firm intention of clasping my hand andpouring out her soul 